title: TinyGo: Fast, Small, Concurrent: Choose Three
subtitle: TinyGo on microcontrollers
abstract: This talk will show using live demos why TinyGo (http://tinygo.org) the Go compiler for "small places" is a excellent choice for next generation IoT and embedded devices.
